In addition, we are not responsible for the data collection, use, disclosure, security policies or security practices of other organizations, such as Facebook, Apple, Google, Microsoft, RIM, or any other app developer, app provider, social media platform provider, operating system provider, wireless service provider, or device manufacturer including with respect to any Personal Data you disclose to other organizations through or in connection with our Apps or Social Media Pages, unless those organizations act in accordance with our instruction or contractual relationship with us.
11.ADVERTISING BY THIRD PARTIES
We use third party advertising companies to provide advertisements about products and services that may attract your interests when you access and use the Services and other websites and online services.
You may receive advertising based on the information related to your access to and use of the Services, other websites or online services on your device, and the information we receive from third parties. These advertising companies place or recognize unique cookies on your browser (including using pixel tags). We also use these technologies, along with the information we obtain about your online usage, to recognize you across the devices you use, such as your mobile phone and laptop computer. For more information about this practice and how to opt out of it for desktop and mobile browsers on specific devices accessing this privacy policy, please visit
http://optout.aboutads.info/#/
or
http://optout.networkadvertising.org/#/
. To opt out on the mobile app, you can download the AppChoices app at
www.aboutads.info/appchoices
.
12.SENSITIVE DATA
Unless we request it, we ask you not to send us any sensitive Personal Data through the Services. Sensitive Personal Data includes, but not limited to, social security numbers, racial or ethnic origin, political opinions, religion or other beliefs, health, biometrics or genetic characteristics, criminal record including criminal proceedings, or trade union membership.
13.THIRD PARTY PAYMENT SERVICE
We may use third party payment services to process payments made through the Services. If you make a payment through such a payment service, your Personal Data will be obtained by such a third party, not by us, and will be subject to the third party's privacy policy, not this privacy policy. We do not control and are not responsible for the collection, use and disclosure of your Personal Data by such third parties.
14.UPDATING OF THIS PRIVACY POLICY
